data.description: Amazing home with plenty of space to raise a family.  This home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac. The location is perfect for quick access to the entertainment of Ocean Springs, Biloxi, and D'Iberville.  This home has walk in closets, crown molding, and space for entertaining or family gatherings. It is only a few minutes away from any of the schools in St. Martin.
